            "text": "and the recompense shall surely happen.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 520,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4682,
            "text": "By the heaven with its passages,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4683,
            "text": "surely, you are in different sayings,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4684,
            "text": "and are turned away from him who is turned.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4685,
            "text": "Woe to the liars",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4686,
            "text": "who are heedless in the immersion.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4687,
            "text": "'When will the Day of Judgement be' they ask.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4688,
            "text": "On that Day they shall be tried at the Fire,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4689,
            "text": "'Taste your trial. This is what you have sought to hasten'",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4690,
            "text": "The righteous shall live among gardens and fountains,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4691,
            "text": "receiving what their Lord will give them because before this they were gooddoers.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4692,
            "text": "They slept but a little at night,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4693,
            "text": "and at dawn would ask forgiveness,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4694,
            "text": "and in their wealth was a share for whosoever asked and for whosoever was prevented.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4695,
            "text": "For those with sure belief there are signs in the earth,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4696,
            "text": "and also in yourselves. Can you not see?",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4697,
            "text": "In the sky is your provision and that which you are promised.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4698,
            "text": "So by the Lord of heaven and earth, it is as true as your speech.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 455,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4699,
            "text": "Have you heard the story of Abraham's honored guests?",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4700,
            "text": "They entered to him and said: 'Peace' And he replied: 'Peace, you are people unknown to me'",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4701,
            "text": "So he turned to his household and brought a fattened calf.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4702,
            "text": "He set it before them, saying: 'Will you not eat'",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4703,
            "text": "Then he conceived a fear about them, and they said: 'Have no fear', and gave him the glad tidings that he was to have a knowledgeable son.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4704,
            "text": "(Sarah) his wife came with an exclamation and clasped her face, and said: 'Surely, I am a barren old woman'",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4705,
            "text": "'Such, says your Lord' they replied: 'He is the Wise, the Knower'",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 26,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 521,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 208,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4706,
            "text": "'Messengers' said he (Abraham), 'what is your errand'",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4707,
            "text": "They replied: 'We are sent to a sinful nation,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4708,
            "text": "so that we bring down stones of clay upon them",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4709,
            "text": "marked by your Lord for the sinful'",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4710,
            "text": "So We brought the believers out of that they were in.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4711,
            "text": "But We found in it only one household of those who had surrendered themselves,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4712,
            "text": "and left therein a sign for those who fear the painful punishment.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4713,
            "text": "In Moses, too, (there were signs). We sent him to Pharaoh with clear authority,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4714,
            "text": "but he turned his back with his Assembly, saying: 'He is (either) a sorcerer or a mad man'",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4715,
            "text": "So We seized him and his hosts and cast them into the sea. Indeed, he was blameworthy.",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4716,
            "text": "And in Aad. We let loose on them a withering wind",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4717,
            "text": "that left nothing it came upon, except that it was ashes.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4718,
            "text": "And in Thamood it was said to them: 'Take your enjoyment for awhile'",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4719,
            "text": "But in their pride they turn away from the commandment of their Lord and the thunderbolt struck them whilst they were looking;",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4720,
            "text": "they could neither stand up straight, nor were they helped.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4721,
            "text": "And before them the nation of Noah, indeed they were a debauched nation.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 456,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4722,
            "text": "We built the heaven with might, and We widely extended it.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4723,
            "text": "and We cradled the earth. And We are the Best of Cradlers.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4724,
            "text": "We created two kinds of all things, so that you will remember.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4725,
            "text": "Therefore, flee to Allah. I am a clear warner to you from Him.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4726,
            "text": "Do not set up with Allah another god. I am a clear warner to you from Him.",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 522,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4727,
            "text": "Similarly, no Messenger came to those before them but they said: 'Sorcerer, or mad'",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4728,
            "text": "Have they handed this down from one to another? No, rather, they are an insolent nation.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4729,
            "text": "So turn away from them, you shall not be blamed,",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4730,
            "text": "But remind, the Reminder will benefit the believers.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4731,
            "text": "I have not created mankind and jinn except to worship Me.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4732,
            "text": "I do not desire provision from them, nor do I desire that they should feed Me.",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4733,
            "text": "Surely, Allah is the Provider, the Possessor of Power, the Mighty.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4734,
            "text": "The evildoers shall have for their portion, a portion like their companions (who were destroyed before them). Therefore, they should not ask Us to hasten!",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4735,
            "text": "Woe then to the unbelievers for their Day which they were promised!",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 457,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 52,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الطُّورِ",
        "englishName": "At-Tur",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Mount",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4736,
            "text": "By the Mount",
