            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4737,
            "text": "and by the Book in lines",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4738,
            "text": "in an exposed parchment",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4739,
            "text": "by the Visited House,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4740,
            "text": "and the uplifted roof",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4741,
            "text": "and the sea that is full",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4742,
            "text": "surely, the punishment of your Lord is about to come,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4743,
            "text": "there is none to prevent it.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4744,
            "text": "Upon the Day when the heaven spins dizzily",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4745,
            "text": "and the mountains move, moving.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4746,
            "text": "On that Day woe to those who belied",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4747,
            "text": "those who are in plunging, playing.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4748,
            "text": "On that Day when they shall be pitched into the Fire of Gehenna (Hell),",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4749,
            "text": "(it will be said to them): 'This is the Fire which you belied!",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 523,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4750,
            "text": "Is this magic, or is it that you do you not see?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4751,
            "text": "Roast in it, bear it with or without patience, it is the same, you are only being recompensed for that which you used to do'",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4752,
            "text": "But in the Gardens the righteous shall live in bliss,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4753,
            "text": "rejoicing in all their Lord has given them, and their Lord will guard them against the punishment of Hell.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4754,
            "text": "(It will be said): 'Eat and drink with a good appetite because of that which you did'",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4755,
            "text": "(They shall be) reclining on couches ranged in rows and We shall wed them to houris (virgins of Paradise) with large wide eyes.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4756,
            "text": "Those who believe, and whose descendants follow in belief, We will join their descendants to them. And We will not reduce them of anything of their deeds. Every one is pledged for what he has earned.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4757,
            "text": "We shall give them fruits and meat as they desire.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4758,
            "text": "There they will pass a goblet to one another with neither idle talk nor sin,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 209,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4759,
            "text": "and youths, of their own, shall pass among them as if they were hidden pearls.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4760,
            "text": "They will go to one another asking each other questions:",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4761,
            "text": "'When we were among our people' they will say, 'we were ever fearful,",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4762,
            "text": "but Allah has been gracious to us and has protected us from the punishment of the burning wind.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4763,
            "text": "Before, we were supplicating to Him. He is the Giving, the Most Merciful'",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 458,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4764,
            "text": "Therefore, remind. By the Favor of Allah, you are neither a soothsayer, nor mad.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4765,
            "text": "Or do they say: 'He is a poet, we are waiting for some misfortune to befall him'",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4766,
            "text": "Say: 'Wait if you will; I shall be waiting with you'",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 524,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4767,
            "text": "Or, do their intellects order them to do this? Or, are they an insolent people?",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4768,
            "text": "Do they say: 'He has invented it' No, they do not believe.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4769,
            "text": "Let them produce a phrase like it, if what they say is true!",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4770,
            "text": "Or, were they created out of nothing? Or, were they their own creators?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4771,
            "text": "Or, did they create the heavens and the earth? No, their belief is not certain!",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4772,
            "text": "Or, are the treasures of your Lord in their keeping? Or, are they the controllers?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4773,
            "text": "Or, do they have a ladder on which they listen? Then let any of them that has listened bring a clear authority.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4774,
            "text": "Or, has He daughters, and they sons?",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4775,
            "text": "Or, do you ask them for a wage, so that they become weighed down in debt?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4776,
            "text": "Or, is the Unseen in their keeping, so they are writing it down?",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4777,
            "text": "Or, do they desire to outwit? The unbelievers are the outwitted.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4778,
            "text": "Or, do they have a god, other than Allah? Exaltations to Allah above that which they associate!",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4779,
            "text": "Even if they saw lumps falling from the sky they would say: 'A massed cloud'",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4780,
            "text": "So leave them till they encounter their Day in which they shall be thunderstruck.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4781,
            "text": "The Day when their guile shall not relieve them a thing, and they shall not be helped.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4782,
            "text": "For the harmdoers there is indeed, a punishment before that, but most of them do not know.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4783,
            "text": "And be patient under the Judgement of your Lord, surely, you are before Our Eyes. And exalt with the praise of your Lord when you arise,",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4784,
            "text": "and exalt Him in the night and at the declining of the stars.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 525,
            "ruku": 459,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 53,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّجۡمِ",
        "englishName": "An-Najm",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Star",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4785,
            "text": "By the star when it plunges,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4786,
            "text": "your companion is neither astray, neither errs,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4787,
            "text": "nor does he speak out of desire.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4788,
            "text": "Indeed it is not except a Revelation which is revealed,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4789,
            "text": "taught by One who is Stern in power.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4790,
            "text": "Of might, he (Gabriel) stood firm",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4791,
            "text": "while he was in the highest horizon;",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4792,
            "text": "then he drew near, and became close",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4793,
            "text": "he was but two bows' length or even nearer,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4794,
            "text": "so (Allah) revealed to His worshiper (Gabriel) that which he revealed (to Prophet Muhammad).",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4795,
            "text": "His heart did not lie of what he saw.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4796,
            "text": "What, will you dispute with him about what he sees!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4797,
            "text": "Indeed, he saw him in another descent",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4798,
            "text": "at the Lote Tree (Sidrat tree) of the ending",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4799,
            "text": "close to the Garden of Refuge.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4800,
            "text": "When there comes to the Lote Tree, that which comes",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4801,
            "text": "his eyes did not swerve, nor did they stray",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4802,
            "text": "for indeed he saw one of the greatest signs of his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4803,
            "text": "(Among the idols) have you considered allat and al'uzza,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4804,
            "text": "and, another, the third manat?",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4805,
            "text": "What, have you males, and He females!",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4806,
            "text": "That is indeed an unjust division.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4807,
            "text": "They are but names, named by you and your fathers. Allah has not sent down any authority for them. They follow conjecture and their soul's desire, eventhough the guidance of their Lord has come to them.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4808,
            "text": "Is the human to have whatever he fancies?",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4809,
            "text": "To Allah belongs the Eternal life and the first life.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 460,
            "hizbQuarter": 210,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4810,
            "text": "How many an angel is there in the heavens whose intercession shall not benefit until Allah gives permission to whom He will and is pleased.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 526,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4811,
            "text": "Those who disbelieve in the Everlasting Life call the angels by female names.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4812,
            "text": "Yet of this they have no knowledge, they follow mere conjecture, and conjecture does not help against truth.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4813,
            "text": "So turn from those who turn away from Our Remembrance and only desire this present life.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4814,
            "text": "That is all they have of knowledge. Your Lord knows best who has strayed from His Path, and those who are guided.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4815,
            "text": "To Allah belongs whatsoever is in the heavens and whatsoever is in the earth. He will recompense the evildoers according to their deeds, and recompense those who have done good with the finest reward",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4816,
            "text": "those who avoid the major sin and indecencies except the small sins, indeed your Lord is of immense forgiveness and He is more knowledgeable of you when He created you from the earth and when you were still unborn in your mothers' wombs. Do not praise yourself. Allah knows the cautious.",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 461,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4817,
            "text": "Have you considered he who turns his back,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4818,
            "text": "and gives a little, grudgingly?",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4819,
            "text": "Or, does he possess knowledge of the Unseen, and can therefore see?",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4820,
            "text": "Or, has he not been told of that which is in the Scrolls of Moses",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4821,
            "text": "and Abraham, who paid his debt in full?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4822,
            "text": "That no soul shall bear another's burden,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4823,
            "text": "and that everyone shall have in his account only that which he worked for,",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4824,
            "text": "and that his work is surely seen",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4825,
            "text": "then, he shall be recompensed for it in full repayment",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4826,
            "text": "and that the final return is to your Lord,",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4827,
            "text": "that it is He who causes to laugh and causes to weep.",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4828,
            "text": "and that it is He who causes to die, and causes to live",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 527,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4829,
            "text": "and that it is He who created pairs, the male and the female,",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4830,
            "text": "from an ejaculated drop (of sperm),",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4831,
            "text": "and that upon Him is the second creation",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4832,
            "text": "and that it is He who gives riches and causes to hoard,",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4833,
            "text": "and that He is the Lord of (the star) Sirius,",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4834,
            "text": "that it was He that destroyed ancient Aad",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4835,
            "text": "and Thamood, sparing no one,",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4836,
            "text": "and before them the nation of Noah, they exceeded in evil and were insolent.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4837,
            "text": "He plunged the villages",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4838,
            "text": "so that there came upon them that which came.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4839,
            "text": "So which then of your Lord's favors do you dispute?",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4840,
            "text": "This is a warner from the warners of ancient times.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4841,
            "text": "The Imminent is near at hand;",
            "numberInSurah": 57,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4842,
            "text": "none except Allah can disclose it.",
            "numberInSurah": 58,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4843,
            "text": "Do you marvel then at this discourse (the Koran)?",
            "numberInSurah": 59,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4844,
            "text": "Or do you laugh, and do you not weep",
            "numberInSurah": 60,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4845,
            "text": "while you are thoughtless?",
            "numberInSurah": 61,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4846,
            "text": "Rather, prostrate to Allah and worship Him.",
            "numberInSurah": 62,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 462,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": {
              "id": 13,
              "recommended": false,
              "obligatory": true
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 54,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Moon",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 4847,
            "text": "The Hour is drawing near, and the moon is split (in two).",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4848,
            "text": "Yet if they see a sign (the unbelievers) turn their backs and say: 'This is but a continuation of sorcery'",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4849,
            "text": "They have belied, and follow their own fancies. But, every issue will be settled!",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4850,
            "text": "Tidings containing a deterrent have come to them",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4851,
            "text": "which are full of wisdom; but the warnings do not help.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4852,
            "text": "Therefore, turn away from them. On the Day when the Caller summons them to a terrible thing,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 528,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4853,
            "text": "their eyes will be humbled as they come out from their graves as if they were scattered locusts,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4854,
            "text": "running (with their necks extended) to the Caller. The unbelievers will say: 'This is indeed a harsh Day'",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 211,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4855,
            "text": "(Long) before them the nation of Noah belied. They belied Our worshiper saying: 'Mad' and he was reprimanded.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4856,
            "text": "Then he supplicated to his Lord, (saying): 'I am overcome, help me'",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4857,
            "text": "We opened the Gates of Heaven with torrential water",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4858,
            "text": "and caused the earth to gush with springs, so that the waters met for a predestined matter.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4859,
            "text": "We carried him in a well built, watertight vessel made from planks (of wood)",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4860,
            "text": "that ran on under Our Eyes, a recompense for him because he had been disbelieved.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4861,
            "text": "We have left it as a sign. Is there any that will remember?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4862,
            "text": "How then were My punishment and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4863,
            "text": "We have made the Koran easy to remember, is there any that will remember!",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4864,
            "text": "Aad too belied. How then were My punishment and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4865,
            "text": "And We sent against them a howling wind in a Day of continuous of ill fortune",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4866,
            "text": "and snatched people up as though they were stumps of uprooted palmtrees.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4867,
            "text": "How then were My punishment and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4868,
            "text": "We have made the Koran easy to remember, is there any that will remember?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 463,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4869,
            "text": "Thamood, too, belied Our warnings.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4870,
            "text": "They said: 'Are we to follow a mortal who is one of us? Then indeed, we would surely be in error and insane.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4871,
            "text": "Out of all of us has the Reminder been given to him alone? Rather, he is indeed an arrogant liar'",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4872,
            "text": "(To him We said): 'Tomorrow they shall know who is the arrogant liar.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4873,
            "text": "We are sending to them as a trial, a shecamel, so watch them and have patience.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 529,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4874,
            "text": "Tell them that the water is to be divided between them, a drink each for them in turn'",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4875,
            "text": "But they called their companion who took hold of her and hamstrung her.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4876,
            "text": "How then were My punishment and My warnings!",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4877,
            "text": "Then We sent against them one Shout and they became like the trampled twigs of the (sheep) penbuilder.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4878,
            "text": "We have made the Koran an easy Remembrance, is there any that will remember!",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4879,
            "text": "The nation of Lot belied Our warnings.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4880,
            "text": "We let loose on all of them a squall of claystones, except for the house of Lot whom We saved at dawn",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4881,
            "text": "through Our Mercy. So it is that We recompense the thankful.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4882,
            "text": "He had warned them of Our assault but they disputed the warnings.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4883,
            "text": "They even solicited of him his guests, but We obliterated their eyes: 'Now, taste My punishment and My warnings'",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4884,
            "text": "And at daybreak a determined punishment came upon them.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4885,
            "text": "'Now, taste My punishment and My warnings'",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4886,
            "text": "We have made the Koran an easy Remembrance, is there any that will remember!",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 464,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4887,
            "text": "The warnings also came to Pharaoh's people,",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4888,
            "text": "but they belied all Our signs so We seized them with the seizing of the Mighty, Powerful.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4889,
            "text": "What then, are your unbelievers better than those? Or do you have an immunity (written) in the Scrolls?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4890,
            "text": "Or do they say: 'We are a gathering that will be victorious'",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4891,
            "text": "Most certainly their gatherings shall be routed, and they will turn their backs.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4892,
            "text": "Rather, the Hour is their encounter. And that Hour will be most calamitous and bitter.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4893,
            "text": "Indeed the wrongdoers are in error and a raging fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4894,
            "text": "On the Day when they are dragged on their faces into the Fire, (it will be said to them): 'Taste the touch of the Scorching'",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4895,
            "text": "Indeed, We have created all things according to a measure.",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 530,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4896,
            "text": "And Our Order is but one word like the flashing of an eye.",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4897,
            "text": "And We destroyed those like you, is there any that will remember!",
            "numberInSurah": 51,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4898,
            "text": "All their deeds are in the Scrolls,",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4899,
            "text": "everything, be it great or small, is recorded.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4900,
            "text": "Indeed, the cautious shall live amid gardens and a river,",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4901,
            "text": "in a secure abode, in the presence of the Powerful King.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 465,
            "hizbQuarter": 212,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
