            "text": "He created the human from clay, like earthenware",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4916,
            "text": "and He created the jinn from smokeless fire.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4917,
            "text": "Which favors of your Lord will you both belie?",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 531,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4918,
            "text": "The Lord of the Two Easts, the Lord of the Two Wests.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 532,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4919,
            "text": "Which favors of your Lord will you both belie?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 532,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4920,
            "text": "He has let forth the two seas, they meet together,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 532,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4921,
            "text": "and between them is a barrier which they do not overpass.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 532,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 4922,
            "text": "Which favors of your Lord will you both belie?",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 27,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 532,
            "ruku": 466,
            "hizbQuarter": 213,
            "sajda": false
