            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5385,
            "text": "No loyal friend will ask another loyal friend",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 568,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5386,
            "text": "though they are in sight of each other. To ransom himself from the punishment of that Day, the sinner will wish that he might even ransom himself by his sons,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5387,
            "text": "his companion (wife), his brother,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5388,
            "text": "the kinsmen who gave him shelter,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5389,
            "text": "and whosoever is in the earth, altogether, so that it might save him.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5390,
            "text": "No, in truth, it is a Furnace!",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5391,
            "text": "It snatches away by the scalps,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5392,
            "text": "and it shall call him who withdrew and turned his back",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 227,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5393,
            "text": "and amassed (riches) and hoarded.",
