            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5402,
            "text": "and go in fear of the punishment of their Lord,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5403,
            "text": "for none is secure from the punishment of their Lord,",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5404,
            "text": "who guard their privates",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5405,
            "text": "except from their wives and what their right hands own, for these they are not blameworthy.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5406,
            "text": "But whosoever seeks beyond that, they are the transgressors.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5407,
            "text": "(Those) who keep their trusts and their covenant,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5408,
            "text": "and standby their witnessing,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5409,
            "text": "and who are constant in their prayers.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5410,
            "text": "Those are highly honored in the Gardens.",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 502,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5411,
            "text": "But what is the matter with the unbelievers, that they strain their glances continuously towards them,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5412,
            "text": "on the right and on the left in groups?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5413,
            "text": "What, is every one of them eager to be admitted to the Garden of Bliss?",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5414,
            "text": "Not at all, for We have created them of what they know.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 569,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5415,
            "text": "No, I swear by the Lord of the Easts and the Wests that We have the ability",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5416,
            "text": "to exchange them with others better than they; nothing can outstrip Us!",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5417,
            "text": "So leave them alone to plunge and play, until they encounter the Day which they are promised;",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5418,
            "text": "the Day when they shall rush from their graves, as if they were hurrying to a raised flag,",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5419,
            "text": "their eyes are humbled and they are covered with humiliation. Such is the Day that they were promised.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 503,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 71,
        "name": "سُورَةُ نُوحٍ",
        "englishName": "Nooh",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Noah",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5420,
            "text": "We sent Noah to his nation, saying: 'Give warning to your nation before a painful punishment overtakes them'",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5421,
            "text": "He said: 'My nation, I am a clear warner for you.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5422,
            "text": "Worship Allah, fear Him, and obey me.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5423,
            "text": "He will forgive you your sins and respite you till an appointed term. When the term of Allah arrives it cannot be deferred; if you but knew'",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5424,
            "text": "'My Lord' said he, 'night and day I have called my nation,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5425,
            "text": "but my call has only increased them in running away.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5426,
            "text": "Each time I called them so that You might forgive them, they thrust their fingers in their ears and wrapped themselves in their garments, and persisted becomingvery proud.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5427,
            "text": "I called to them clearly,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5428,
            "text": "and indeed, I spoke to them both publicly and in secret:",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5429,
            "text": "'Ask for forgiveness of your Lord,' I said. 'Surely, He is the Forgiver.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 570,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5430,
            "text": "He will let loose the sky upon you in abundance",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5431,
            "text": "and give to you wealth and sons, and provide you with gardens and rivers.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5432,
            "text": "What is the matter with you that you do not want the Greatness of Allah,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5433,
            "text": "He has created you by stages!",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5434,
            "text": "Have you not seen how Allah created the seven heavens one above the other,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5435,
            "text": "setting in them the moon as a light and the sun as a lantern?",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5436,
            "text": "Allah has caused you to grow out of the earth,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5437,
            "text": "and to it He will return you. Then, He will bring you forth.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5438,
            "text": "Allah has made the earth spread out for you",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5439,
            "text": "so that you walk in its spacious paths.'",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 504,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5440,
            "text": "Noah said: 'My Lord, they have rebelled against me and followed he whose wealth and offspring increase him only in loss,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5441,
            "text": "they have devised a mighty plot,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5442,
            "text": "and said: 'Do not renounce your gods, do not leave waddan or suwa'an or yaghutha, or ya'uqa, or nasra'",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5443,
            "text": "And they have led many astray. (Noah supplicated saying): 'Allah, do not increase the harmdoers except in error'",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5444,
            "text": "So because of their sins they were drowned and admitted into the Fire. They found none to help them other than Allah.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5445,
            "text": "And Noah (supplicated) saying: 'My Lord, do not leave a single unbeliever upon the earth.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5446,
            "text": "Surely, if You leave them they will mislead Your worshipers and father none but the immoral, and unbelievers.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5447,
            "text": "Forgive me, My Lord, and my parents, and whosoever seeks refuge in my house as a believer, and the believers men and women alike, and do not increase the harmdoers except in ruin'",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 571,
            "ruku": 505,
            "hizbQuarter": 228,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 72,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الجِنِّ",
        "englishName": "Al-Jinn",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Jinn",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5448,
            "text": "Say: 'It is revealed to me that a party of jinn listened then said: 'We have indeed heard a wonderful Koran,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5449,
            "text": "that guides to the Right Path. We believe in it and we will not associate anyone with our Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5450,
            "text": "He exalted be the Majesty of our Lord, who has neither taken to Himself a wife, nor a son!",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5451,
            "text": "The ignorant fool among us has spoken outrageously against Allah,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5452,
            "text": "we never thought that either human or jinn would ever tell a lie against Allah!'",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5453,
            "text": "But there were certain men from mankind who would take refuge with certain males from the jinn and they increased them in tyranny.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5454,
            "text": "Like you, they thought that Allah would never raise the dead.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5455,
            "text": "(The jinn continued saying): 'We made our way towards heaven, but we found it filled with stern guards and a flame.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5456,
            "text": "There, we would sit to eavesdrop, but now an eavesdropper finds a flame in wait for him.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5457,
            "text": "And so we do not know whether evil is intended for those on earth, or whether their Lord intends to guide them.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5458,
            "text": "Some of us are righteous, but some are otherwise, we are sects that differ.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5459,
            "text": "We know that we cannot frustrate Allah in the earth, nor can we frustrate Him by flight.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5460,
            "text": "When we heard the Guidance, we believed in it, and whosoever believes in his Lord shall fear neither shortage nor injustice.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 572,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5461,
            "text": "Some of us have surrendered (Muslims) and some of us have deviated. Those who surrendered sought the Right Path,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5462,
            "text": "but those who have deviated shall become the fuel of Gehenna (Hell).",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5463,
            "text": "If they had followed the Path We would give to them abundant water to drink,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5464,
            "text": "and tested them with it. And whosoever turns away from his Lord's Remembrance, He will hurl him into a stern punishment.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5465,
            "text": "Mosques belong to Allah, so do not call to anyone else, other than Allah.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5466,
            "text": "When the worshiper of Allah stood supplicating to Him, they swarmed around him (Prophet Muhammad).",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 506,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5467,
            "text": "Say: 'I supplicate only to my Lord and I do not associate any with Him'",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5468,
            "text": "Say: 'Indeed, I possess no power over you, either for harm or for guidance'",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5469,
            "text": "Say: 'None shall protect me from Allah, and other than Him, I will find no refuge,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5470,
            "text": "except a deliverance from Allah and His Messages. He who disobeys Allah and His Messenger, for him is the Fire of Gehenna, which he will be in for ever.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5471,
            "text": "When they see that which they were promised they shall know who is weaker in helpers and fewer in numbers.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5472,
            "text": "Say: 'I do not know whether that which you are promised is near, or whether my Lord will set for it a time.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 573,
            "ruku": 507,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5473,
