            "number": 5547,
            "text": "Indeed, each one of them desires to be given unrolled scrolls.",
            "numberInSurah": 52,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5548,
            "text": "No, indeed they have no fear of the Everlasting Life.",
            "numberInSurah": 53,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5549,
            "text": "No, indeed, surely, this is a Reminder.",
            "numberInSurah": 54,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5550,
            "text": "So, whoever wills, will remember it.",
            "numberInSurah": 55,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5551,
            "text": "But none will remember, unless Allah wills, He is the Owner of fear, the Owner of forgiveness.",
            "numberInSurah": 56,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 511,
            "hizbQuarter": 230,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 75,
        "name": "سُورَةُ القِيَامَةِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Qiyaama",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Resurrection",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5552,
            "text": "No! I swear by the Day of Resurrection,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5553,
            "text": "No! I swear by the reproachful soul!",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5554,
            "text": "What, does the human think We shall never gather his bones?",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5555,
            "text": "Indeed yes, We are able to shape his fingerstips yet again!",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5556,
            "text": "Rather, the human desires to continue in his immorality,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5557,
            "text": "'When will the Day of Resurrection be' he asks,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5558,
            "text": "but when the sight is dazed",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5559,
            "text": "and the moon eclipsed,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5560,
            "text": "when the sun and moon are gathered together",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5561,
            "text": "on that Day the human will ask: 'To (which place) shall I flee'",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5562,
            "text": "No, there shall be no (place of) refuge.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5563,
            "text": "For on that Day the refuge shall be to your Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5564,
            "text": "On that Day the human shall be informed of his former and latter deeds.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5565,
            "text": "He shall be a clear proof against himself,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5566,
            "text": "even though he offers his excuses.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5567,
            "text": "Do not move your tongue with it (the Revelation) to hasten it.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5568,
            "text": "It's gathering and reciting is upon Us.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5569,
            "text": "When We recite it, follow its recitation.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5570,
            "text": "It's explanation is upon Us.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5571,
            "text": "Yet you love this hasty world",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5572,
            "text": "and are heedless of the Everlasting Life.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5573,
            "text": "On that Day there shall be radiant faces,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5574,
            "text": "gazing towards their Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5575,
            "text": "And on that Day there shall be scowling faces,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5576,
            "text": "so they might think the Calamity had been inflicted upon them.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5577,
            "text": "But, when (the soul) reaches the collar bone",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5578,
            "text": "and it is said: 'Who is a healing chanter'",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5579,
            "text": "and when he thinks it is the time of departure",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5580,
            "text": "and when leg is intertwined with leg,",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5581,
            "text": "upon that Day the driving shall be to your Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5582,
            "text": "Because, he neither believed nor prayed;",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5583,
            "text": "he belied the truth and turned away;",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5584,
            "text": "then went arrogantly to his household.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5585,
            "text": "Near to you and nearer,",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5586,
            "text": "then nearer to you and nearer!",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5587,
            "text": "Does the human think he will be left to roam at will?",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5588,
            "text": "What, was he not an ejaculated drop (of sperm)?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5589,
            "text": "Then he was a clot of blood, then He created and formed him",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5590,
            "text": "and made from him two kinds, male and female.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5591,
            "text": "What, is He then unable to revive the dead?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 76,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الإِنسَانِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Insaan",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Man",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5592,
            "text": "Indeed, there came upon the human a period of time when he was an unremembered thing.",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5593,
            "text": "We have created the human from a (sperm) drop, a mixture, testing him; We made him to hear and see.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5594,
            "text": "Indeed, We have guided him to the path, he is either grateful or ungrateful.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5595,
            "text": "Indeed, for the unbelievers We have prepared chains, fetters and a Blazing (Fire).",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5596,
            "text": "But the righteous shall drink of a goblet mixed with camphor;",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5597,
            "text": "a fountain at which the worshipers of Allah drink and make it gush forth abundantly;",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5598,
            "text": "they who keep their vows and fear a Day whose evil is spread;",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5599,
            "text": "who give food, for the love of Him to the needy, the orphan, and the captive,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5600,
            "text": "(saying): 'We feed you only desirous of the Face of Allah; we seek of you neither recompense nor thanks,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5601,
            "text": "for we fear from our Lord a stern, frownful Day'",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5602,
            "text": "So Allah will save them from the evil of that Day and has secured for them radiance and joyfulness,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5603,
            "text": "and recompense them for their patience with a Garden, and robes of silk.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5604,
            "text": "Reclining there upon couches, they shall see neither the sun nor the moon.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5605,
            "text": "Near them shall be its shades with its clusters hung gently down,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5606,
            "text": "and passed around them shall be silver vessels, and crystal goblets,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5607,
            "text": "goblets of silver that they have precisely measured.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5608,
            "text": "And they shall be given to drink from a cup whose mixture is ginger,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5609,
            "text": "from a fountain called Salsabila.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5610,
            "text": "Immortal youths will go about them, when you see them, you would suppose them to be scattered pearls.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5611,
            "text": "When you see them, you see bliss, and a great Kingdom.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5612,
            "text": "Upon them there will be garments of green silk, rich brocade, and they will be adorned with bracelets of silver. Their Lord will give them a pure beverage to drink.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5613,
            "text": "'See, this is your recompense, your striving is thanked'",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5614,
            "text": "We have indeed, sent down to you the Koran, a (clear) sending,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5615,
            "text": "therefore be patient under the Judgement of your Lord, and do not obey either the sinner or the unbeliever.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5616,
            "text": "And, remember the Name of your Lord at the dawn and in the evening;",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5617,
            "text": "and in the night prostrate to Him; and exalt Him for a long night.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5618,
            "text": "Indeed, these love the hasty life, and are heedless and leave behind them a heavy Day.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5619,
            "text": "We created them, and We strengthened their joints, but, when We will, We shall indeed exchange their likes.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5620,
            "text": "This is indeed a Reminder, so that he who will, takes a path to his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5621,
            "text": "Yet you will not unless Allah wills; surely, Allah is the Knower, the Wise.",
