            "text": "noble and pious.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5775,
            "text": "Perish the human! How unthankful he is!",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5776,
            "text": "From what did He create him?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5777,
            "text": "From a (sperm) drop He created him and then determined him,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5778,
            "text": "then eased his path for him,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5779,
            "text": "then causes him to die and buries him,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5780,
            "text": "then, He will raise him when He wills.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5781,
            "text": "Indeed, he has not fulfilled that which He has ordered him.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5782,
            "text": "Let the human reflect on the food he eats,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5783,
            "text": "how We pour down rain in abundance,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5784,
            "text": "and split the earth, splitting,",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5785,
