      {
        "number": 82,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الانفِطَارِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Infitaar",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Cleaving",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5830,
            "text": "When the sky is split,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5831,
            "text": "when the planets are scattered,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5832,
            "text": "when the oceans are gushed forth,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5833,
            "text": "when the graves are overturned,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5834,
            "text": "the soul shall know what it has done, the former and the latter.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5835,
            "text": "O human! What has deceived you concerning your Generous Lord",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5836,
            "text": "who created you, formed you and proportioned you?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5837,
            "text": "In whatever shape He will He could surely have fashioned you.",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5838,
            "text": "Rather, you belied the Recompense.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5839,
            "text": "Yet over you there are watchers,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5840,
            "text": "noble scribes",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5841,
            "text": "who know of all that you do.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5842,
            "text": "Indeed, the righteous shall (live) in bliss.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5843,
            "text": "But the wicked, indeed they shall be in the Fiery Furnace,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5844,
            "text": "roasting in it on the Day of Recompense",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5845,
            "text": "and from it they shall never be absent.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5846,
            "text": "What could let you know what the Day of Recompense is!",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5847,
            "text": "Again, what could let you know what the Day of Recompense is!",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5848,
            "text": "It is the Day when no soul can do a thing for another soul. That Day, the command belongs to Allah.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 524,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 83,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Defrauding",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5849,
            "text": "Woe to the diminishers,",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5850,
            "text": "who, when people measure for them, take full measure,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5851,
            "text": "but when they measure or weigh for others, they reduce!",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5852,
            "text": "Do they not think that they will be resurrected",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5853,
            "text": "for a great Day,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5854,
            "text": "the Day when people will stand before the Lord of the Worlds?",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 587,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5855,
            "text": "No indeed, the Book of the immoral is in Sijjeen.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5856,
            "text": "What could let you know what the Sijjeen is!",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5857,
            "text": "(It is) a marked Book.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5858,
            "text": "Woe on that Day to those who belied it,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5859,
            "text": "who belied the Day of Recompense!",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5860,
            "text": "None belies it except every guilty sinner.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5861,
            "text": "When Our verses are recited to him, he says: 'Fictitious tales of the ancients'",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5862,
            "text": "No indeed! Their own deeds have cast a veil over their hearts.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5863,
            "text": "No indeed, on that Day they shall be veiled from their Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5864,
            "text": "Then they shall roast in Hell,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5865,
            "text": "and it will be said to them: 'This is that which you belied'",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5866,
            "text": "But, the Book of the righteous is in the 'Illiyoon.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5867,
            "text": "What could let you know what the 'Illiyoon is!",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5868,
            "text": "(It is) a marked Book,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5869,
            "text": "witnessed by those who are near (to Allah).",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5870,
            "text": "The righteous shall indeed be blissful,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5871,
            "text": "(reclining) upon couches they will gaze,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5872,
            "text": "and in their faces you shall know the radiance of bliss.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5873,
            "text": "They shall be given to drink of a wine that is sealed,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5874,
            "text": "its seal is musk, for this let the competitors compete;",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5875,
            "text": "and its mixture is Tasneem,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5876,
            "text": "a fountain at which those brought near (to their Lord) drink.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5877,
            "text": "The sinners laughed at the believers",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5878,
            "text": "and winked at one another as they passed them by.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5879,
            "text": "When they returned to their people they returned jesting;",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5880,
            "text": "and when they saw them said: 'These are they who are astray'",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5881,
            "text": "Yet they were not sent to be their guardians.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5882,
            "text": "But on this Day the believers will laugh at the unbelievers",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 588,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5883,
            "text": "as they (recline) upon their couches and gaze (around them).",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5884,
            "text": "Have the unbelievers been rewarded for what they did?",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 589,
            "ruku": 525,
            "hizbQuarter": 235,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
