            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5915,
            "text": "when they were seated around it",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5916,
            "text": "and they were witnesses of what they did to the believers",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5917,
            "text": "and their revenge on them was only because they believed in Allah, the Almighty, the Praised,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 590,
            "ruku": 527,
            "hizbQuarter": 236,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5918,
            "text": "to whom belongs the Kingdom of the heavens and earth. And Allah is the Witness of all things.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
