            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6004,
            "text": "They were tyrants in the land",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6005,
            "text": "and exceeded in corruption therein.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6006,
            "text": "(Therefore) your Lord let loose upon them a scourge of punishment;",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6007,
            "text": "indeed, your Lord is ever watchful.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6008,
            "text": "As for man, when his Lord tests him by honoring him and favoring him, he says: 'My Lord, has honored me'",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6009,
            "text": "But when He tests him by restricting his provision, he says: 'My Lord has humiliated me'",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6010,
            "text": "No! But you show no good to the orphan,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6011,
            "text": "nor do you urge one another to feed the needy.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6012,
            "text": "and you devour the inheritance with greed,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6013,
            "text": "and you ardently love wealth.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6014,
            "text": "No! But when the earth quakes and is pounded,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6015,
            "text": "and your Lord comes with the angels, rank upon rank,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6016,
            "text": "and Gehenna (Hell) is brought near on that Day the human will remember, and how shall the Reminder be for him?",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6017,
            "text": "He will say: 'Would that I had forwarded (good works) for my life!'",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6018,
            "text": "But on that Day none will punish as He (Allah) will punish,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6019,
            "text": "nor will any bind as He binds.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6020,
            "text": "O satisfied soul,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6021,
            "text": "return to your Lord wellpleased, wellpleasing.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6022,
            "text": "Join My worshipers and",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6023,
            "text": "enter My Paradise!",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 90,
        "name": "سُورَةُ البَلَدِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Balad",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The City",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 6024,
            "text": "No, I swear by this country (Mecca),",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6025,
            "text": "and you are a lodger in this country.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6026,
            "text": "And by the giver of birth, and whom he fathered,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6027,
            "text": "We created the human in fatigue.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6028,
            "text": "Does he think that none has power over him!",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6029,
            "text": "He will say: 'I have destroyed a vast wealth'",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6030,
            "text": "Does he think that none has observed him?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6031,
            "text": "Have We not given him two eyes,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6032,
            "text": "a tongue, and two lips,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6033,
            "text": "and guided him on the two paths (of good and evil)?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6034,
            "text": "Yet he has not scaled the height.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6035,
            "text": "What could let you know what the height is!",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6036,
            "text": "(It is) the freeing of a slave,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6037,
            "text": "the giving of food upon the day of hunger",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6038,
            "text": "to an orphaned relative",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6039,
            "text": "or to a needy person in distress;",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6040,
            "text": "so that he becomes one of those who believe, charge each other to be patient, and charge each other to be merciful.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6041,
            "text": "Those are the Companions of the Right.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6042,
            "text": "But those who disbelieve in Our verses, they are the Companions of the Left,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6043,
            "text": "with the Fire closed above them.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 594,
            "ruku": 532,
            "hizbQuarter": 238,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
