            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6149,
            "text": "by the dawnraiders,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6150,
            "text": "raising a trail of dust,",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6151,
            "text": "dividing the gathering.",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6152,
            "text": "Indeed, the human is ungrateful to his Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6153,
            "text": "To this he himself shall bear witness.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6154,
            "text": "And indeed he is ardent for the love of good (wealth, becoming greedy).",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 239,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6155,
            "text": "Does he not know that when that which is in the graves is overthrown,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 599,
            "ruku": 542,
            "hizbQuarter": 240,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6156,
            "text": "and that which is in the chest is brought out,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
